83 #define SET_VAR(group, variable, value) do { \
84  if (!compareEqual(group->variable, value)) \
85  group.access().variable = value; \
86  } while (0)
87 
88 #define SET_NESTED_VAR(group, parentVariable, variable, value) do { \

90  group.access().parentVariable.access().variable = value; \
91  } while (0)

1991 inline void RenderStyle::NonInheritedFlags::copyNonInheritedFrom(const NonInheritedFlags& other)
1992 {
1993  // Only a subset is copied because NonInheritedFlags contains a bunch of stuff other than real style data.
1994  uint64_t nonInheritedMask = overflowMask << overflowXOffset
1995  | overflowMask << overflowYOffset
1996  | clearMask << clearOffset
1997  | displayMask << effectiveDisplayOffset
1998  | positionMask << positionOffset
1999  | displayMask << originalDisplayOffset
2000  | unicodeBidiMask << unicodeBidiOffset
2001  | verticalAlignMask << verticalAlignOffset
2002  | floatingMask << floatingOffset
2003  | oneBitMask << explicitInheritanceOffset
2004  | tableLayoutBitMask << tableLayoutOffset
2005  | hasViewportUnitsBitMask << hasViewportUnitsOffset;
2006 
2007  m_flags = (m_flags & ~nonInheritedMask) | (other.m_flags & nonInheritedMask);
2008 }
